She opened her link. "Drillbit, we are expecting a few bots who need 
a CR chamber. Make them check in thier weapons at the entrance and 
see them to the CR room. Thank you."


She walked back down the hall and into the conference room with 
Aracnia. "Forgive my abrupt departure earlier. Now, back to busines. 
What do you think of my plan? We can have Megatron assist us and 
destroy the maximals. He is powerful and wishes to get rid of them as 
much as we do. And as long as he behaves, he will sit on the council 
with us. If not, we simply..a..remove him from his seat."
She sat down and looked at Aracnia.
